{"image_id": "MKC_2012_page_61", "image_size": [1275, 1650], "ocr": [{"text": "McCormick & Company    2012 Annual Report    page 57", "bbox": [876.4, 1582.7, 1150.0, 1601.9]}, {"text": "U.S. Deﬁned Contribution Retirement Plans", "bbox": [125.0, 109.2, 466.1, 132.1]}, {"text": "For the U.S. McCormick 401(k) Retirement Plan, we match 100%", "bbox": [125.0, 132.4, 583.1, 155.0]}, {"text": "of a participant’s contribution up to the ﬁrst 3% of the participant’s", "bbox": [125.0, 155.4, 597.7, 177.9]}, {"text": "salary, and 50% of the next 2% of the participant’s salary. In addition,", "bbox": [125.0, 178.3, 604.8, 200.8]}, {"text": "we make contributions for U.S. employees not covered by the deﬁned", "bbox": [125.0, 201.2, 600.4, 223.7]}, {"text": "beneﬁt plan. Some of our smaller U.S. subsidiaries sponsor separate", "bbox": [125.0, 224.1, 604.5, 246.7]}, {"text": "401(k) retirement plans. Our contributions charged to expense under", "bbox": [125.0, 247.0, 604.4, 269.6]}, {"text": "all 401(k) retirement plans were $7.4 million, $7.0 million and $6.8", "bbox": [125.0, 269.9, 587.5, 292.5]}, {"text": "million in 2012, 2011 and 2010, respectively.", "bbox": [125.0, 292.8, 431.7, 315.4]}, {"text": "At the participant’s election, 401(k) retirement plans held 2.6 million", "bbox": [125.0, 338.7, 603.3, 361.2]}, {"text": "shares of McCormick stock, with a fair value of $170.4 million, at", "bbox": [125.0, 361.6, 581.2, 384.1]}, {"text": "November 30, 2012. Dividends paid on these shares in 2012 were", "bbox": [125.0, 384.5, 585.1, 407.0]}, {"text": "$3.4 million.", "bbox": [125.0, 407.4, 210.0, 430.0]}, {"text": "Postretirement Beneﬁts Other Than Pensions", "bbox": [125.0, 452.9, 483.1, 475.8]}, {"text": "We currently provide postretirement medical and life insurance ben-", "bbox": [125.0, 476.1, 601.1, 498.7]}, {"text": "eﬁts to certain U.S. employees who were covered under the active", "bbox": [125.0, 499.0, 593.8, 521.6]}, {"text": "employees’ plan and retire after age 55 with at least ﬁve years of", "bbox": [125.0, 522.0, 586.4, 544.5]}, {"text": "service. The subsidy provided under these plans is based primarily", "bbox": [125.0, 544.9, 590.7, 567.4]}, {"text": "on age at date of retirement. These beneﬁts are not pre-funded but", "bbox": [125.0, 567.8, 598.7, 590.3]}, {"text": "paid as incurred. Employees hired after December 31, 2008 are not", "bbox": [125.0, 590.7, 594.5, 613.3]}, {"text": "eligible for a company subsidy. They are eligible for coverage on an", "bbox": [125.0, 613.6, 596.0, 636.2]}, {"text": "access-only basis.", "bbox": [125.0, 636.5, 251.7, 659.1]}, {"text": "Our other postretirement beneﬁt expense follows:", "bbox": [125.0, 671.9, 473.5, 694.5]}, {"text": "(millions)", "bbox": [125.0, 715.6, 174.9, 733.1]}, {"text": "2012", "bbox": [451.8, 714.0, 489.4, 733.4]}, {"text": "2011", "bbox": [511.1, 714.6, 554.0, 733.4]}, {"text": "2010", "bbox": [569.5, 714.6, 597.2, 733.4]}, {"text": "Service cost", "bbox": [125.0, 743.3, 201.8, 763.3]}, {"text": "$ 4.0", "bbox": [447.9, 742.7, 483.3, 763.3]}, {"text": "$ 3.8", "bbox": [508.3, 743.3, 541.7, 763.3]}, {"text": "$ 5.0", "bbox": [566.7, 743.3, 600.0, 763.3]}, {"text": "Interest costs", "bbox": [125.0, 764.1, 210.6, 784.2]}, {"text": "4.9", "bbox": [464.8, 763.5, 483.3, 784.2]}, {"text": "4.5", "bbox": [523.2, 764.1, 541.7, 784.2]}, {"text": "5.0", "bbox": [581.5, 764.1, 600.0, 784.2]}, {"text": "Amortization of prior service costs", "bbox": [125.0, 785.0, 340.6, 805.0]}, {"text": "(4.0)", "bbox": [460.2, 784.4, 488.0, 805.0]}, {"text": "(5.9)", "bbox": [519.5, 785.0, 545.4, 805.0]}, {"text": "(5.5)", "bbox": [577.8, 785.0, 603.7, 805.0]}, {"text": "Amortization of losses", "bbox": [125.0, 805.8, 265.3, 825.8]}, {"text": "—", "bbox": [466.7, 805.2, 483.3, 825.8]}, {"text": "0.7", "bbox": [523.2, 805.8, 541.7, 825.8]}, {"text": "1.3", "bbox": [581.5, 805.8, 600.0, 825.8]}, {"text": "Special termination beneﬁts", "bbox": [125.0, 826.6, 300.8, 846.7]}, {"text": "(0.1)", "b