"text": "2015", "bbox": [668.8, 264.1, 698.4, 284.1]}, {"text": "7.0", "bbox": [960.7, 264.1, 979.2, 284.1]}, {"text": "1.2", "bbox": [1046.1, 264.1, 1064.6, 284.1]}, {"text": "8.2", "bbox": [1131.5, 264.1, 1150.0, 284.1]}, {"text": "2016", "bbox": [668.8, 284.9, 698.4, 305.0]}, {"text": "7.1", "bbox": [960.7, 284.9, 979.2, 305.0]}, {"text": "1.2", "bbox": [1046.1, 284.9, 1064.6, 305.0]}, {"text": "8.3", "bbox": [1131.5, 284.9, 1150.0, 305.0]}, {"text": "2017", "bbox": [668.8, 305.7, 698.4, 325.8]}, {"text": "7.2", "bbox": [960.7, 305.7, 979.2, 325.8]}, {"text": "1.3", "bbox": [1046.1, 305.7, 1064.6, 325.8]}, {"text": "8.5", "bbox": [1131.5, 305.7, 1150.0, 325.8]}, {"text": "2018–2022", "bbox": [668.8, 326.6, 736.3, 346.6]}, {"text": "37.1", "bbox": [953.3, 326.6, 979.2, 346.6]}, {"text": "6.5", "bbox": [1046.1, 326.6, 1064.6, 346.6]}, {"text": "43.6", "bbox": [1124.1, 326.6, 1150.0, 346.6]}, {"text": "The assumed discount rate was 3.8% and 5.2% for 2012 and", "bbox": [668.8, 371.5, 1101.6, 394.0]}, {"text": "2011, respectively.", "bbox": [668.8, 394.4, 797.3, 416.9]}, {"text": "For 2013, the assumed annual rate of increase in the cost of covered", "bbox": [668.8, 440.2, 1150.4, 462.8]}, {"text": "health care beneﬁts is 7.6% (8.4% last year). It is assumed to", "bbox": [668.8, 463.1, 1118.9, 485.7]}, {"text": "decrease gradually to 5.0% in the year 2021 (5.0% in 2019 last year)", "bbox": [668.8, 486.0, 1150.8, 508.6]}, {"text": "and remain at that level thereafter. A one percentage point increase", "bbox": [668.8, 508.9, 1148.3, 531.5]}, {"text": "or decrease in the assumed health care cost trend rate would have", "bbox": [668.8, 531.9, 1139.2, 554.4]}, {"text": "an immaterial effect on the beneﬁt obligation and the total of service", "bbox": [668.8, 554.8, 1149.5, 577.3]}, {"text": "and interest cost components for 2012.", "bbox": [668.8, 577.7, 941.4, 600.2]}, {"text": "9. STOCK-BASED COMPENSATION", "bbox": [668.8, 623.2, 945.6, 646.1]}, {"text": "We have three types of stock-based compensation awards: restricted", "bbox": [668.8, 658.9, 1153.1, 681.5]}, {"text": "stock units (RSUs), stock options and company stock awarded as", "bbox": [668.8, 681.8, 1125.2, 704.4]}, {"text": "part of our mid-term incentive program (MTIP). Total stock-based", "bbox": [668.8, 704.7, 1126.6, 727.3]}, {"text": "compensa tion expense for 2012, 2011 and 2010 was $20.2 million,", "bbox": [668.8, 727.7, 1135.2, 750.2]}, {"text": "$13.0 million and $11.9 million, respectively. Total unrecognized", "bbox": [668.8, 750.6, 1112.7, 773.1]}, {"text": "stock-based compensation expense at November 30, 2012 was $13.3", "bbox": [668.8, 773.5, 1154.2, 796.0]}, {"text": "million and the weighted-average period over which this will be rec-", "bbox": [668.8, 796.4, 1143.3, 819.0]}, {"text": "ognized is 1.4 years.", "bbox": [668.8, 819.3, 809.1, 841.9]}, {"text": "For all awards, forfeiture rates are considered in the calculation of", "bbox": [668.8, 865.1, 1135.3, 887.7]}, {"text": "compensation expense.", "bbox": [668.8, 888.0, 832.5, 910.6]}]}